	]b
	": LOL this level name. I take a weird route to the box in the left wing so that the dantini doesn't see me too early and kill me while I'm pounding the box. Unfortunately, because of his head turning cycles, this means I can't get him to hit me any earlier than he does. Rest of the level is pretty straight forward if I remember correctly. I finally get down to 0 lives here, just before a ton of lives in the next five levels. Also, why does world 3 have no color crystal skips while the other worlds each have 2-3?
	$LF
