	]b
	": This guy has really funky AI, that can be messed with using tail attacks at the right frames. Also, apparently Croc has watched some SM64 and learned how to BLJ (it only works in this room because of the weird wall design, if you are wondering why I don't use it elsewhere).
	$LF
